Class TreeNode<T>

java.lang.Object
TreeNode<T>
Type Parameters:
T - 
public class TreeNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object
This generic class is used in the MorseCodeTree classes. The class consists of a reference to the data and a reference to the left and the right child.
